{"tid":2237812,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"支那人行將遠期售滙業務外滙風險準備金率下調為0","createTime":"2020-10-10T14:49:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T04:33:45.000Z","uid":126731,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"5339616b51359ace9f9761358a4e100496724d31","tid":2237812,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T14:49:59.000Z","msg":"咁即係代表D乜呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;水退就知邊個裸泳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSOURCE@信報<br />\n<br />\n中國人民銀行公布，決定自今年10月12日起，將遠期售滙業務的外滙風險準備金率從20%下調為0。<br />\n<br />\n人行表示，今年以來，人民幣滙率以市場供求為基礎雙向浮動，彈性增強，市場預期平穩，跨境資本流動有序，外滙市場運行保持穩定，市場供求平衡，為此，自下周一(12日)起，將遠期售滙業務的外滙風險準備金率從20%下調為0。<br />\n<br />\n人行稱，下一步，人行將繼續保持人民幣滙率彈性，穩定市場預期，保持人民幣滙率在合理均衡水平上的基本穩定。"},{"pid":"f2156750d5ee9fd1b9b21273bcaefc3c9d91bcf2","tid":2237812,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T14:52:08.000Z","msg":"0% <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"097adcdad0e89b7500ffeaeba0aa9c30f7512735","tid":2237812,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f2156750d5ee9fd1b9b21273bcaefc3c9d91bcf2","tid":2237812,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T14:52:08.000Z","msg":"0% <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T14:52:41.000Z","msg":"將來可唔可以負數？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef7e5c5593779b48b9a83b3a828692b3a5a2a4f","tid":2237812,"uid":6030,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T14:53:54.000Z","msg":"即係點？"},{"pid":"2294f58965a828b26978349b9ed5cf2c8ca063e7","tid":22378